 Singles Sales Chart number ones|UK<br>Sales]]<br><ref>Peaks on the UK Singles Sales Chart\n\n* \"Strange\": {{Cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/singles-sales-chart/2020221/7509/|title=Official Singles Sales Chart Top 100: 21 February 2020|publisher=[[Official Charts Company]]|access-date=22 February 2020}}\n* \"Stop This Flame\": {{Cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/singles-sales-chart/20200214/7509/|title=Official Singles Sales Chart Top 100: 14 February 2020|publisher=Official Charts Company|access-date=14 February 2020}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[UK Singles Downloads Chart|UK<br>Down.]]<br><ref>Peaks on the UK Singles Downloads Chart:\n* \"Strange\": {{Cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/singles-downloads-chart/20200221/7000/|title=Official Singles Downloads Chart Top 100: 21 February 2020|publisher=[[Official Charts Company]]|url-status=live|access-date=22 February 2020}}\n* \"Stop This Flame\": {{Cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/singles-downloads-chart/20200214/7000/|title=Official Singles Downloads Chart Top 100: 14 February 2020|website=Official Charts Company|url-status=live|access-date=7 February 2020}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Ultratop|BEL<br>(FL)]]<br><ref name=\"FL\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.ultratop.be/nl/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Celeste+%5BUK%5D|title=Discografie Celeste [UK]|website=[[Ultratop]]|url-status=live|access-date=17 January 2020}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Ultratop|BEL<br>(WA)]]<br><ref name=\"FL\" />\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Dutch Top 40|NL]]<br><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.top40.nl/top40-artiesten/celeste|title=Celeste: Top 40-hits|website=[[Dutch Top 40]]|language=nl|url-status=live|access-date=15 February 2020}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Scottish Singles and Albums Charts|SCO]]<br><ref>