\n|47\n|14\n|12\n|5\n|7\n|21\n|12\n|-\n| colspan=\"10\" style=\"font-size:90%\" |\"&#x2014;\" denotes releases that did not chart, or charted on a subchart.\n|}\n\n==== As featured artist ====\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! Title\n! Year\n! Album/EP\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"30,000 Feet\"<br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(Jeshi featuring Celeste)</span>\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2020\n|''Bad Taste''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Times Like These (song)#Live Lounge Allstars charity single|Times Like These]]\"<br/><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(as part of [[Times Like These (song)#Artists|Live Lounge Allstars]])</span>\n| {{n/a|Non-album single}}\n|-\n|}\n\n=== SoundCloud releases ===\n\n* ''Celeste'' \u2013 EP (2014; {{Small|no longer available}})\n\n=== Music videos ===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:15em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:0.5em;\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:27em;\"| Director(s)\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:1em;\"| {{abbr|Ref.|References}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Lately\"<br>{{Small|(featuring Gotts Street Park)}}\n| rowspan=\"8\"| 2019\n|Sam Hiscox\n|<ref>{{cite web|author=Celeste [confirmed account]|title=Celeste \u2013 Lately (Official Video)|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4WGHP2K5K2Q|via=[[YouTube]]|access-date=28 November 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Lately feat. Gotts Street Park (Music Video) by Celeste|url=https://music.apple.com/us/music-video/lately-feat-gotts-street-park/1449290639|work=[[Apple Music]]|access-date=28 November 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Father's Son\"\n|Bob Harlow\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.broadwayworld.com/bwwmusic/article/UK-Breakout-Celeste-Debuts-Fathers-Son-Video-20190128|title=U.K. Breakout Celeste Debuts 'Father's Son' Video|last=BWW News Desk|date=28 January 2019|website=[[BroadwayWorld.com]]|access-date=28 November 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Coco Blood\"\n|Akinola Davids (a.k.a. Crack Stevens)\n|<ref name=\":16\" />\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Strange (Live)\"\n|Colin Solal Cardo\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Celeste \u2013 Strange (Live Session \u2013 La Blogoth\u00e8que)|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nx0nJbCf5p4|via=[[YouTube]]|publisher=La Blogoth\u00e8que|access-date=28 November 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Celeste: Chapter 1\"\n|[[Universal Music Group|UMG]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Celeste: Chapter 1 by Celeste|url=https://music.apple.com/us/music-video/celeste-chapter-1/1481478646|work=[[Apple Music]]|access-date=28 November 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Strange\" (Lyric Video)\n|Celeste Waite\n|<ref>{{cite web|author=Celeste|title=Celeste \u2013 Strange (Lyric Video)|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i5XHTHaH80E|via=[[YouTube]]|access-date=28 November 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"You Do Something to Me\"<br>{{Small|(with [[Paul Weller]])}}\n|Colin Solal Cardo\n|<ref>{{cite web|author=Celeste|title=Celeste & Paul Weller \u2013 You Do Something To Me (Live)|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lUPsKZfuXi8|via=[[YouTube]]|access-date=28 November 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Strange (Celeste song)#Music video|Strange]]\"\n|Silent Tapes\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Stop This Flame#Music video|Stop This Flame]]\"\n|2020\n|Leonn Ward\n|\n|}\n\n== Filmography ==\n=== Television ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!Year\n!Title\n!Role\n!Notes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" |2019\n|''Inas Nacht''\n| rowspan=\"8\" |Herself\n|Episode: 2 November 2019\n|-\n|''[[Later... with Jools Holland]]''\n|Episode: [[List of Later... with Jools Holland episodes#Series 54|24 October 2019]]\n|-\n|''[[C \u00e0 vous]]''\n|Episode: 11 December 2019\n|-\n|''[[Top of the Pops]]''\n|Episode: [[List of performers on Top of the Pops#2019|30 December 2019]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" |2020\n|''[[The Late Late Show with James Corden]]''\n|Episode: [[List of The Late Late Show with James Corden episodes (2020)#January|29 January 2020]]\